different statistics--

00:18:42.520 --> 00:18:45.150
Boltzmann statistics,
Bose-Einstein statistics, Fermi

00:18:45.150 --> 00:18:46.410
statistics.

00:18:46.410 --> 00:18:54.000
And it gives you the result
