00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:55.750
you have the factor of 2.

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:57.830
For fermions, of
course, you get 0.

00:18:57.830 --> 00:19:02.630
The average between bosons
2 and fermions 0 is 1.

00:19:02.630 --> 00:19:06.330
And this is the
classical statistics.

